1 (b) Volunteers for such determination;
2 (14) Nothing in this section shall be deemed to deprive a woman of all appropriate
3 medical care necessary to prevent her physical death;
4 (15) "Adult day-care center" means any adult care facility which provides part-time care,
5 day or night, but less than twenty-four (24) hours, to at least four (4) adults not
6 related to the operator of the adult care facility by blood, marriage, or adoption.
